The Public Protector's office has released a transcript detailing the conversation between Thuli Madonsela, President Jacob Zuma &amp; his lawyers. JOHANNESBURG - President Jacob Zuma and former Public Protector Thuli Madonsela's have never really been the best of friends, especially in recent months.Their political duel has played out in public during both during and after Madonsela's tenure.The cut and thrust of their power play has commanded the attention of the South African public.And one of the final interactions between the two makes for interesting reading.Read the full transcript below. Annexure A1 by Primedia Broadcasting on Scribd